import { loadTheme } from 'office-ui-fabric-react';

export default loadTheme({
  palette: {
    themePrimary: '#ffffff',
    themeLighterAlt: '#767676',
    themeLighter: '#a6a6a6',
    themeLight: '#c8c8c8',
    themeTertiary: '#d0d0d0',
    themeSecondary: '#dadada',
    themeDarkAlt: '#eaeaea',
    themeDark: '#f4f4f4',
    themeDarker: '#f8f8f8',
    neutralLighterAlt: '#363c48',
    neutralLighter: '#353b47',
    neutralLight: '#333944',
    neutralQuaternaryAlt: '#2f353f',
    neutralQuaternary: '#2d323c',
    neutralTertiaryAlt: '#2b303a',
    neutralTertiary: '#c8c8c8',
    neutralSecondary: '#d0d0d0',
    neutralPrimaryAlt: '#dadada',
    neutralPrimary: '#ffffff',
    neutralDark: '#f4f4f4',
    black: '#f8f8f8',
    white: '#373d49',
  }
});
